description:
Reserved matters application seeking approval of appearance, landscaping, layout and scale for Phase 3 of Mill Hill East development pursuant to Outline planning permission reference H/04017/09 dated: 22/9/2011 involving the erection of 138 units 7 x 5 bedroom houses, 41 x 4 bedroom houses, 47 x 3 bedroom houses, 26 x 2 bedroom apartments and 17 x 1 bedroom apartments together with details to discharge the requirements of:
Conditions 5 (Reserved matter details), 8 (Affordable housing), 12 (Noise Survey along Boundary with IBSA House), 26(Access points), 27 (Details of Estate Roads), 29(Internal access roads), 35 (Petrol/oil interceptors), 48(Open space), 52 (Children's playing space), 57 (Boundary treatment/buffer), 70 (Home standards), 80 (Sustainable homes), 83 (Grey water/rainwater recycling),85 (Green/brown roofs).
decision_conditions: CON05 - Time Limit on Full Permission
